  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PwBuilding
    Used to manage a list of PwFloor objects for a building.
    PwCoordinateSpace
    A PwCoordinateSpace is used to manage a dimensions for a map; such as width, height and scale.
    PwFloor
    Used to manage a list of PwFloorResource objects for a building.
    PwFloorResource
    Used to manage an image representing the floor.
    PwMarker
    Use this PwMarker to add custom markers on a PwMapView.
    PwPoint
    Used for point data that belongs to a building.
    PwRoute
    Used for route data.
    PwVenue
    Used for Venue data.
